HEADWORD: payslip
<hw>pay"slip`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a slip of paper
included with a person's salary payment, that records how much money the
person has earned and how much tax or insurance etc. has been taken
out.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

